titleInfo.title: USA v. Schmeling
titleInfo.subTitle: JUDGMENT as to Jolyn Schmeling. The defendant plead guilty to Count I of the Indictment and is sentenced to Probation for 5 Years with special conditions of Supervision; $100.00 Special Assessment; Restitution in the amount of $60,724.25. Criminal Case Terminated as to defendant Jolyn Schmeling. Ordered by Judge Joseph F. Bataillon. - (1 cc to USM)(KBJ)
